      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, systemic stuff is important for the context section. but for the actual data synthesis part, i need to be able to cite the specific trends. like, don't you have access to the raw statistical patterns that show which groups are being arrested or convicted at higher rates? i'm not asking about the \"why\" yet, just the \"what\"—can you provide the breakdown of what the current datasets actually show regarding those disparities?",
